---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service — Utilifyer"
  description="Terms of Service for Utilifyer.com. Read our terms before using our free online tools."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8">Last updated: April 24, 2025</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing or using Utilifyer.com ("the Site"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Site.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p>Utilifyer.com provides a collection of free, browser-based utility tools including calculators, converters, generators, and other productivity tools. All tools are provided free of charge and run entirely in your browser.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">3. Use of the Service</h2>
        <p>You agree to use the Site only for lawful purposes. You must not:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Use the Site in any way that violates applicable laws or regulations</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the Site or its infrastructure</li>
          <li>Use automated means (bots, scrapers) to access the Site in a way that places excessive load on our servers</li>
          <li>Reproduce, duplicate, copy, or resell any part of the Site without our express written permission</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">4. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p>The Site and all tools are provided "as is" and "as available" without any warranties of any kind, express or implied. We do not warrant that:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>The Site will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of viruses</li>
          <li>The results of any tool are accurate, complete, or suitable for any particular purpose</li>
          <li>Any errors in the Site will be corrected</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">Tool results (calculations, conversions, etc.) are for informational and educational purposes only. Always verify important results with a qualified professional before making financial, medical, legal, or other significant decisions.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, Utilifyer.com and its operators shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of (or inability to use) the Site or any tool therein, even if we have been advised of the possibility of such damages.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content, design, code, and trademarks on the Site are the property of Utilifyer.com unless otherwise indicated. You may not reproduce or redistribute any content without prior written consent, except for personal, non-commercial use.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">7. Third-Party Links and Advertising</h2>
        <p>The Site may display third-party advertisements (Google AdSense) and may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or accuracy of any third-party sites. The presence of an advertisement does not constitute endorsement.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">8. Privacy</h2>
        <p>Your use of the Site is also governed by our <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>, which is incorporated into these Terms by reference.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of the Site after changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">10. Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about these Terms, please <a href="/contact" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">contact us</a>.</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
